* errors.c: Source code included by lab0.c that handles the formatting of errors.
* Makefile: Makefile with clean, check, + dist options
* README: This file!

## Check functionality
I check the return values of 3 cases: input error for a nonexistent file, output error for a file without write permissions & catching the segfault error.